          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μέτρον</span></b> : <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">measure,
            measuring-rod</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 12.422</span></i>;
          then of any vessel and its contents, <i><span class="en">Il.
